        <UserObject label="依赖" mermaidId="e:房源统计概况-&gt;房源#0" mermaidBaseStyle="curved=1;dashed=1;startArrow=none;endArrow=classic;endSize=9;strokeColor=light-dark(#333333,#cccccc);html=1;fontSize=16;labelBackgroundColor=light-dark(#ECECFF,#1f2020);fontFamily=Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Arial,sans-serif;fontColor=light-dark(#333333,#cccccc);exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0.32;entryY=0;" mermaidBaseValue="依赖" id="7eVDWPtCOEXNINBA27vf-1780">
